## Problem
In `src/utils.ts:100`, there's a magic number:

```typescript
if (counter > 1000) {
  throw new Error('Too many archive collisions...');
}
```

And in `src/main.ts:79`:
```typescript
const maxRetries = 3;
```

## Suggested Fix
Extract to named constants at the top of each file:

```typescript
// utils.ts
const MAX_COLLISION_ATTEMPTS = 1000;

// main.ts  
const MAX_RENAME_RETRIES = 3;
```

This makes the code more self-documenting and easier to adjust if needed.

